{"tid":2065510,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"有無人聽台灣音樂？","createTime":"2020-06-15T15:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T22:24:45.000Z","uid":360830,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b87a5d95378da28ee1374a667e23d7dff67b57","tid":2065510,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"遊走主流同獨立之間的口味，以下全部認真推介<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WEYFqCUze8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9WEYFqCUze8&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=176e5c22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9WEYFqCUze8</a><br />\n告五人《紅》<br />\n- 呢隊野男、女主音把聲都好掂，快歌慢歌一樣掂<br />\n- 耳朵遲鈍，對我嚟講佢把聲同魏如萱無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 感人MV，完整故事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHFWlckPR-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFHFWlckPR-E&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=24881274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FHFWlckPR-E</a><br />\nMary See the Future《Cheer》<br />\n- 情感障礙，我睇呢個MV係睇到差D喊<br />\n- 好多歌都感受到隊band的搖滾魂，雖然有時覺得主唱把聲死魚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 諗咗好耐點解係Mary See the Future而唔係Mary Sees the Future，一係 subjunctive mood，一係台仔D英文...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VGHLqi_mxnk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVGHLqi_mxnk&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=3498fef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VGHLqi_mxnk</a><br />\n魏如萱《Don't Cry Don't Cry》<br />\n- 自從陳綺貞移民做咗吸金星人之後，魏如萱就成為我心目中嘅台灣第一女聲<br />\n- 佢都忽忽地(褒義)，連姨媽到同老豆支筆都可以作首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 出道到依家包括(自然捲樂團)所有歌都正，陳綺貞頂多聽到華麗的冒險就完了，完<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gl9vmdmMJN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgl9vmdmMJN0&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=31fdaba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gl9vmdmMJN0</a><br />\n原子邦妮《在名為未來的波浪裡》<br />\n- 以前想用電子音樂引朋友走出流行音樂的框框，一直搵唔啱推介，女孩與機器人，Lali Puna, Royksopp, M83全部效果麻麻，直接推Crystal Castles呢D更加死梗，而家唔駛煩，一定係推原子邦妮<br />\n- D MV其實都幾針對音樂文青風格，「我係唔聽廣東歌架」D friend <br />\n- 已加入滾石唱片，嚴格來講唔算獨立音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=saccx5dTmKU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dsaccx5dTmKU&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=5f675cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=saccx5dTmKU</a><br />\n大象體操《FINGER &amp; 中途Midway》<br />\n- 台灣第一Math Rock，不多講<br />\n- 我都係因為呢條連結認識大港開唱，然後多謝韓國魚，搞咗1x年既高雄最強音樂節正式收皮<br />\n- 諗諗下已經唔算pop同indie之間嘅嘢，不過算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YYNPArbfNgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYYNPArbfNgQ&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=ac4f9d84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YYNPArbfNgQ</a><br />\n拍謝少年《暗流》<br />\n- progressive rock?<br />\n- 唔識台語，但聽到好high，淨聽intro已經出水，中後段直頭不德鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 聽完呢首歌再聽d pop band，高下立見<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VVN9wnTa-GQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVVN9wnTa-GQ&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=927c7893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VVN9wnTa-GQ</a><br />\n顯然樂隊《鑰匙掉了誰來救我》<br />\n- 氣質大媽迷幻搖滾，希望你哋get到我想講乜 (女主唱其實好有氣質) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 可以留意下呢隊樂隊的歌詞，都幾露骨辛辣<br />\n<em>一隻髒兮兮的狗在打量我<br />\n我想起我那 辛苦了一生的爸爸媽媽 - 《低賤的人》</em><br />\n- LP名《我最討厭搖滾樂》會心微笑了一嘢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7H52yGup84A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7H52yGup84A&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=ca9a7e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7H52yGup84A</a><br />\n脆樂團 《轉圈圈》<br />\n- 停唔到，係咁睇住條女轉呼拉圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 個intro同旋律熟口熟面，但又up唔出邊度聽過，The Pains of Being Pure at Heart?<br />\n- 總之MV條女又靚又有氣質，係無波<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3N8bzRD6Tno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3N8bzRD6Tno&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=5871dbea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3N8bzRD6Tno</a><br />\n理想混蛋《不是因為天氣晴朗才愛你》<br />\n- 其實我當佢pop咁聽，不過好聽就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 幾首出名既情歌(行星、平衡木)加埋聽，覺得把聲都幾真摯到肉<br />\n- 可能主唱是hehe，所以歌詞果份辛酸咁更加強烈？<br />\n<em>我獨自盤旋在看得見你的軌道<br />\n仰望著你一圈再一圈的圍繞<br />\n我不能靠近 卻也不願遠離<br />\n習慣在你影子裡遊戲我的孤寂 - 《行星》</em><br />\n(聽《行星》即刻諗起《水星記》，神作，不過好似大陸的)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDSf3QoK3uQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaDSf3QoK3uQ&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=ac6141ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDSf3QoK3uQ</a><br />\n洪安妮《我喜歡你》<br />\n- 聽完理想混蛋把真摯男聲，心諗：真摯女聲會諗起邊個？第一時間就出咗呢首歌<br />\n- 諗唔到3個point，就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z7hyNxqVwFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ7hyNxqVwFw&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=46f2921b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z7hyNxqVwFw</a><br />\n鄭宜農《千千萬萬》<br />\n- 聽完hehe的歌不如又聽下sheshe的歌<br />\n- 呢首歌令我即時聯想到M83首Midnight City，有興趣上網搵搵<br />\n- 永遠懷念長髮鄭宜農<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5xwFCtDc0fI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5xwFCtDc0fI&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=97f485cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5xwFCtDc0fI</a><br />\n落日飛車《我的金桔》<br />\n- 第一次接觸呢首歌同MV嘅感覺係，JMLY???????<br />\n- 不過細心聽又覺得幾正，但D 音效聲真係有D on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 唔知點解諗起D 8, 90年代嘅港產殭屍片，唔好問我點解<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wcp4VAAM468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWcp4VAAM468&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=0c627f79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wcp4VAAM468</a><br />\n沒有才能《還是要有長頸鹿才能》<br />\n- 由細到大都唔鍾意聽RAP，不過呢首歌完全接受到，明明混把呀～呀～呀~女聲好普通，但好受落<br />\n- 街聲長冠歌曲<br />\n- 歌名諗起異世界輕小說D書名，唔好問點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9mH-OZ2B-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz9mH-OZ2B-Y&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=63cc3c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9mH-OZ2B-Y</a><br />\nDSPS《我會不會又睡到下午了》<br />\n- 之前開PO介紹《Folk Song For You》，今次介紹另一首<br />\n- 日系清新，剩係呢首歌就諗起Texas Pandaa的Days<br />\n- 團員換人都換得幾密下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dec365e2e9ec380bd48240f3d11c9939a78c009","tid":2065510,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704cc68c6a9e51e358157b479fbd6bc4efe9de74","tid":2065510,"uid